# 🧱 Brick Breaker Game (Java)

## 📌 Project Description
Brick Breaker is a classic arcade-style game developed using Java Swing and Graphics.
The player controls a paddle to bounce the ball and break bricks to score points.

## 🚀 Features
- Paddle controlled by keyboard
- Ball movement physics
- Brick collision detection
- Score tracking
- Game Over system

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- Java
- Swing (JFrame, JPanel)
- Graphics API
- OOP principles

## 🎮 Game Controls
LEFT ARROW  → Move Paddle Left  
RIGHT ARROW → Move Paddle Right

## ▶ How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Open the project in Eclipse / IntelliJ
3. Run the Main class

